{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-novel-version-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon; Novel Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-03",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/themaltesefalconnovel_2603_librivox/maltesefalcon_03_hammett_128kb.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "Three Women",
  "reader_name": "NLizer",
  "page_num": 3,
  "page_total": 4,
  "page_start_sec": 483.48,
  "page_end_sec": 724.82,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.658,
  "corrected": "claude",
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 483.48,
      "end": 484.38,
      "text": "He took out his lighter,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 484.52,
      "end": 485.66,
      "text": "snapped on the flame,"
    },
    {
      "start": 485.8,
      "end": 487.38,
      "text": "and applied it to the end of his cigarette."
    },
    {
      "start": 487.62,
      "end": 488.94,
      "text": "\"You're an angel,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 489.14,
      "end": 490.7,
      "text": "he said tenderly through smoke,"
    },
    {
      "start": 491.36,
      "end": 491.76,
      "text": "\"a nice,"
    },
    {
      "start": 491.76,
      "end": 492.76,
      "text": "rattle-brained angel.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 493.36,
      "end": 495.12,
      "text": "She smiled a bit wryly.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 495.78,
      "end": 496.06,
      "text": "\"Oh,"
    },
    {
      "start": 496.12,
      "end": 496.7,
      "text": "am I?"
    },
    {
      "start": 497.66,
      "end": 500.54,
      "text": "Suppose I told you that your Iva hadn't been home many minutes"
    },
    {
      "start": 500.66,
      "end": 503.82,
      "text": "when I arrived to break the news at three o'clock this morning?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 505.16,
      "end": 505.94,
      "text": "\"Are you telling me?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 506.14,
      "end": 506.96,
      "text": "he asked."
    },
    {
      "start": 507.52,
      "end": 508.6,
      "text": "His eyes had become alert"
    },
    {
      "start": 509.1,
      "end": 510.58,
      "text": "though his mouth continued to smile."
    },
    {
      "start": 511.84,
      "end": 513.38,
      "text": "\"She kept me waiting at the door while",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 513.38,
      "end": 515.08,
      "text": "she undressed or finished undressing."
    },
    {
      "start": 515.28,
      "end": 517.92,
      "text": "I saw her clothes where she had dumped them on a chair."
    },
    {
      "start": 518.42,
      "end": 520.06,
      "text": "Her hat and coat were underneath."
    },
    {
      "start": 520.86,
      "end": 522.9,
      "text": "Her singlet, on top, was still warm."
    },
    {
      "start": 523.5,
      "end": 524.72,
      "text": "She said she had been asleep,"
    },
    {
      "start": 524.94,
      "end": 525.84,
      "text": "but she hadn't."
    },
    {
      "start": 526.64,
      "end": 527.8,
      "text": "She had wrinkled up the bed,"
    },
    {
      "start": 527.94,
      "end": 529.5,
      "text": "but the wrinkles weren't mashed down.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 530.688,
      "end": 532.36,
      "text": "Spade took the girl's hand and patted it.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 533.152,
      "end": 533.66,
      "text": "\"You're a detective,"
    },
    {
      "start": 533.84,
      "end": 534.18,
      "text": "darling,"
    },
    {
      "start": 534.38,
      "end": 534.92,
      "text": "but\"—"
    },
    {
      "start": 535.28,
      "end": 536.32,
      "text": "he shook his head—"
    },
    {
      "start": 537.06,
      "end": 537.88,
      "text": "\"she didn't kill him.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 539.296,
      "end": 540.8,
      "text": "Effie Perine snatched her hand away.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 541.48,
      "end": 542.84,
      "text": "\"That louse wants to marry you,"
    },
    {
      "start": 542.96,
      "end": 543.16,
      "text": "Sam,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 543.46,
      "end": 544.46,
      "text": "she said bitterly."
    },
    {
      "start": 545.28,
      "end": 548.32,
      "text": "He made an impatient gesture with his head and one hand.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 549.36,
      "end": 550.74,
      "text": "She frowned at him and demanded:"
    },
    {
      "start": 551.44,
      "end": 553.1,
      "text": "\"Did you see her last night?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 553.78,
      "end": 554.4,
      "text": "\"No.\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 555.06,
      "end": 556.04,
      "text": "\"Honestly?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 556.72,
      "end": 557.5,
      "text": "\"Honestly."
    },
    {
      "start": 558.304,
      "end": 559.18,
      "text": "Don't act like Dundy,"
    },
    {
      "start": 559.24,
      "end": 559.58,
      "text": "sweetheart."
    },
    {
      "start": 560.16,
      "end": 561.22,
      "text": "It ill becomes you.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 562.4,
      "end": 563.64,
      "text": "\"Has Dundy been after you?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 564.704,
      "end": 565.08,
      "text": "\"Uh-huh.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 566.26,
      "end": 569.02,
      "text": "He and Tom Polhaus dropped in for a drink at four o'clock.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 570.18,
      "end": 572.58,
      "text": "\"Do they really think you shot this what's-his-name?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 573.34,
      "end": 574.0,
      "text": "\"Thursby.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 574.36,
      "end": 576.18,
      "text": "He dropped what was left of his cigarette"
    },
    {
      "start": 576.18,
      "end": 578.42,
      "text": "into the brass tray and began to roll another."
    },
    {
      "start": 579.56,
      "end": 579.94,
      "text": "\"Do they?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 580.6,
      "end": 581.14,
      "text": "she insisted."
    },
    {
      "start": 582.42,
      "end": 582.9,
      "text": "\"God knows.\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 583.27,
      "end": 585.34,
      "text": "His eyes were on the cigarette he was making."
    },
    {
      "start": 586.14,
      "end": 587.76,
      "text": "\"They did have some such notion.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 587.96,
      "end": 590.06,
      "text": "I don't know how far I talked them out of it.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 591.14,
      "end": 591.48,
      "text": "\"Look at me,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 591.54,
      "end": 591.82,
      "text": "Sam.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 593.02,
      "end": 594.14,
      "text": "He looked at her and laughed",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 594.48,
      "end": 594.84,
      "text": "so that,"
    },
    {
      "start": 594.94,
      "end": 595.54,
      "text": "for the moment,"
    },
    {
      "start": 595.7,
      "end": 597.98,
      "text": "merriment mingled with the anxiety in her face."
    },
    {
      "start": 599.0,
      "end": 599.84,
      "text": "\"You worry me,\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 600.02,
      "end": 600.72,
      "text": "she said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 601.15,
      "end": 603.7,
      "text": "seriousness returning to her face as she talked."
    },
    {
      "start": 604.54,
      "end": 606.94,
      "text": "\"You always think you know what you're doing,"
    },
    {
      "start": 607.68,
      "end": 609.6,
      "text": "but you're too slick for your own good,"
    },
    {
      "start": 610.08,
      "end": 612.64,
      "text": "and some day you're going to find it out.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 613.14,
      "end": 616.8,
      "text": "He sighed mockingly and rubbed his cheek against her arm.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 617.952,
      "end": 618.98,
      "text": "\"That's what Dundy says,"
    },
    {
      "start": 619.37,
      "end": 621.4,
      "text": "but you keep Iva away from me,"
    },
    {
      "start": 621.44,
      "end": 621.68,
      "text": "sweet,"
    },
    {
      "start": 622.08,
      "end": 623.34,
      "text": "and I'll manage to survive the"
    },
    {
      "start": 623.34,
      "end": 624.1,
      "text": "rest of my troubles.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 624.64,
      "end": 626.6,
      "text": "He stood up and put on his hat."
    },
    {
      "start": 627.54,
      "end": 629.36,
      "text": "\"Have the _Spade & Archer_ taken off the door"
    },
    {
      "start": 629.5,
      "end": 630.7,
      "text": "and _Samuel Spade_ put on."
    },
    {
      "start": 631.42,
      "end": 633.26,
      "text": "I'll be back in an hour, or phone you.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 634.432,
      "end": 635.44,
      "text": "Spade went through the St.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 635.5,
      "end": 635.88,
      "text": "Mark's"
    },
    {
      "start": 635.96,
      "end": 638.32,
      "text": "long purplish lobby to the desk and asked a"
    },
    {
      "start": 638.32,
      "end": 641.02,
      "text": "red-haired dandy whether Miss Wonderly was in."
    },
    {
      "start": 641.64,
      "end": 643.34,
      "text": "The red-haired dandy turned away,"
    },
    {
      "start": 643.98,
      "end": 644.56,
      "text": "and then back"
    },
    {
      "start": 644.64,
      "end": 645.52,
      "text": "shaking his head."
    },
    {
      "start": 645.78,
      "end": 647.36,
      "text": "\"She checked out this morning,"
    },
    {
      "start": 647.56,
      "end": 647.7,
      "text": "Mr."
    },
    {
      "start": 647.76,
      "end": 648.12,
      "text": "Spade.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 648.32,
      "end": 648.42,
      "text": "\"Thanks.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 650.912,
      "end": 654.76,
      "text": "Spade walked past the desk to an alcove off the lobby where a plump,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 654.94,
      "end": 656.6,
      "text": "young-middle-aged man in dark clothes"
    },
    {
      "start": 656.6,
      "end": 659.24,
      "text": "sat at a flat-topped mahogany desk."
    },
    {
      "start": 659.99,
      "end": 660.86,
      "text": "On the edge of the"
    },
    {
      "start": 660.86,
      "end": 662.62,
      "text": "desk facing the lobby was a triangular"
    },
    {
      "start": 662.62,
      "end": 665.5,
      "text": "prism of mahogany and brass inscribed"
    },
    {
      "start": 665.62,
      "end": 665.76,
      "text": "_Mr."
    },
    {
      "start": 666.36,
      "end": 666.7,
      "text": "Freed_."
    },
    {
      "start": 667.84,
      "end": 671.08,
      "text": "The plump man got up and came around the desk holding out his hand.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 672.32,
      "end": 674.5,
      "text": "\"I was awfully sorry to hear about Archer,"
    },
    {
      "start": 674.52,
      "end": 674.9,
      "text": "Spade,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 675.04,
      "end": 675.5,
      "text": "he said"
    },
    {
      "start": 676.1,
      "end": 677.84,
      "text": "in the tone of one trained to sympathize"
    },
    {
      "start": 677.9,
      "end": 679.19,
      "text": "readily without intrusiveness."
    },
    {
      "start": 679.89,
      "end": 681.5,
      "text": "\"I've just seen it in the _Call_."
    },
    {
      "start": 682.03,
      "end": 683.82,
      "text": "He was in here last night,"
    },
    {
      "start": 683.86,
      "end": 684.22,
      "text": "you know.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 684.86,
      "end": 684.96,
      "text": "\"Thanks,"
    },
    {
      "start": 685.46,
      "end": 685.82,
      "text": "Freed."
    },
    {
      "start": 685.98,
      "end": 687.14,
      "text": "Were you talking to him?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 687.93,
      "end": 688.48,
      "text": "\"No.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 688.74,
      "end": 692.04,
      "text": "He was sitting in the lobby when I came in early in the evening."
    },
    {
      "start": 692.48,
      "end": 693.3,
      "text": "I didn't stop."
    },
    {
      "start": 693.58,
      "end": 695.2,
      "text": "I thought he was probably working,"
    },
    {
      "start": 695.34,
      "end": 697.96,
      "text": "and I know you fellows like to be left alone when you're busy."
    },
    {
      "start": 698.92,
      "end": 700.74,
      "text": "Did that have anything to do with his—?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 701.66,
      "end": 702.5,
      "text": "\"I don't think so,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 702.56,
      "end": 703.72,
      "text": "but we don't know yet."
    },
    {
      "start": 704.26,
      "end": 704.7,
      "text": "Anyway,"
    },
    {
      "start": 704.9,
      "end": 706.52,
      "text": "we won't mix the house up in it"
    },
    {
      "start": 706.54,
      "end": 707.32,
      "text": "if it can be helped.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 708.06,
      "end": 708.78,
      "text": "\"Thanks.\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 710.112,
      "end": 710.58,
      "text": "\"That's all right.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 710.7,
      "end": 713.24,
      "text": "Can you give me some dope on an ex-guest,"
    },
    {
      "start": 713.52,
      "end": 715.3,
      "text": "and then forget that I asked for it?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 715.78,
      "end": 716.48,
      "text": "\"Surely.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 717.96,
      "end": 719.64,
      "text": "\"A Miss Wonderly checked out this morning.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 720.06,
      "end": 721.05,
      "text": "I'd like to know the details.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 722.3,
      "end": 722.56,
      "text": "\"Come along,\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 722.78,
      "end": 723.24,
      "text": "Freed said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 723.44,
      "end": 724.82,
      "text": "\"and we'll see what we can learn.\""
    }
  ]
}
